content: The exam is this Thursday! Here is the [Exam 1 Study Guide](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IzhBXF3IzrsdnuC5oEa3keVPZ9QbXK0HPXMDAAnWPZk/edit?usp=sharing) which includes a section on how I made the exam. I have also released a practice exam on Prairie Learn. We will go over the practice exam during lecture Tuesday.
HW2 coding is now graded. Unlike the exam, there was no partial credit if your code did not compile. For the exam question, I will manually grade code that doesn't get 100%
